Class AddOn.ExtensionRunRequirements

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zaproxy.zap.control.AddOn.BaseRunRequirements
      • org.zaproxy.zap.control.AddOn.ExtensionRunRequirements
  • Enclosing class:
    AddOn

    public static class AddOn.ExtensionRunRequirements
extends AddOn.BaseRunRequirements
    The requirements to run an extension (with add-on dependencies).

    It can be used to check if an extension can or not be run, which requirements it has (for example, dependency add-ons) and which issues prevent it from being run, if any.

    Since:
    2.4.0
